Class GuidanceSpeedPresenter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.msdkui.guidance.base.BaseGuidancePresenter
      • com.here.msdkui.guidance.GuidanceSpeedPresenter

  • public class GuidanceSpeedPresenter
extends BaseGuidancePresenter
    This class creates GuidanceSpeedData instances during guidance and notifies it's listeners about that.
